Package: zeitgebeR
Type: Package
Title: Machine Learning Enhancements for the Philips Hue Lighting System
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Justin Brantley <fascinatingfingers@icloud.com>
Maintainer: Justin Brantley <fascinatingfingers@icloud.com>
URL: https://github.com/fascinatingfingers/zeitgebeR
Description: This package contains functions to support a machine learning
  pipeline for your Philips Hue lighting system that continuously adjusts the
  lighting to match the time of day, current weather conditions, and learned
  preferences. See the README at
  <https://github.com/fascinatingfingers/zeitgebeR/README.md>.
